You will be a key player in the IT Strategy & Planning Team and you enjoy working in an international (virtual) environment with a team of around 100 IT professionals supporting N&B. You will report directly to the Strategy & Planning Lead and in addition also work closely with the CIO.       Senior Procurement Manager, Indirect Procurement  Bang & Olufsen A/S, Kgs. Lyngby or Struer Join us to manage and develop your own category of suppliers. This will be your chance to not only run your own projects but also to develop the category strategy.   As our new Senior Procurement Manager, you will join the Indirect Procurement team in our office in either Struer or Lyngby, Denmark.   Here, you will drive and execute procurement activities within your categories in close corporation with internal stakeholders. This involves scouting for new suppliers, contracting, negotiation and keeping updated with market development. You will also be a key contributor in promoting a cost-conscious mindset across the company.
